Specifications for initial phase of course project:

1. The project will prompt the user for five items of data:
	name, address, city, state, zip

2. This info will be appended to end of text file, all on 
	one line, seperated by ":" charecter

3. Store the name of text file in a variable name "fname"

4. Display the contents of the file and the num. of records
	in the file

5. exit
